ent-RMCSmartGunCO = M56C 'cavalier' smart gun
    .desc = The actual firearm in the Smart Gun System. Back order only. Besides a more robust weapons casing, an ID lock system and a fancy paintjob, the gun's performance is identical to the standard-issue M56B.

